what-people-said-own-words: Nantsi into ethethwa ngabantu ngawabo amazwi.
women-informed-consent: Bonke abasetyhini kwiphulo banike imvume enolwazi.
respondents-informed-consent: Bonke abaphenduli kwiphulo banikeze imvume enolwazi.
pmn01a-data-displayed-survey: Idatha eboniswe kule dashboard iqokelelwa ngokuthe ngqo kwiimpendulo zesaveyi kwaye ayiveli kwizibalo zelizwe elisemthethweni okanye iiseti zedatha. Imele izimvo ezivakaliswe ngabantu abatsha ngexesha lophando, kwaye naziphi na izigqibo ezithathwe kwezi mpendulo zixanduva lomsebenzisi, kungekhona i-PMNCH. I-PMNCH izibophelele ekuhlonipheni, ekukhuthazeni nasekukhuseleni amalungelo kunye nokuphila kakuhle kwabo bonke abantu. Naziphi na iimbono ezivakaliswe kwiimpendulo zesaveyi okanye izinto ezipapashiweyo ezivela kule dashboard eziphikisana nesi sibophelelo azixhaswa yi-PMNCH.
wra03a-question-asked: Umbuzo ubuzile: Sesiphi isicelo sakho esinye seenkonzo ezisemgangathweni zokuzala kunye nokhathalelo lwempilo yoomama?
midwife-question-asked: Umbuzo ubuzile: Yintoni eyona nto uyifunayo kwindima yakho yokuba ngumbelekisi?
pmn01a-question-asked: Umbuzo ubuziwe: Ukuphucula impilo yam, ndifuna...
click-bubble-country-information: Cofa ilivo ukuguqula amaqamza, cofa amaqamza ukujonga ulwazi lwelizwe.
wra03a-click-view-topic-responses: Cofa kwisihloko ukujonga iimpendulo. Amanye amabhinqa akhankanya ngaphezu kwesinye isihloko. Hambisa ngaphezulu kwebar ukuze ubone amanani kunye negama lodidi.
click-view-topic-responses: Cofa kwisihloko ukujonga iimpendulo. Abanye abaphenduli bakhankanye ngaphezu kwesinye isihloko. Hambisa ngaphezulu kwebar ukuze ubone amanani kunye negama lodidi.
to-protect-anonymity: Ukukhusela ukungaziwa, abanye abaphendulayo basusiwe kule dashboard.
wra03a-subtext: Ukufikelela kwiimpendulo ezivulelekileyo ezisi-1.2 sezigidi ngokusebenzisa le dashbhodi isebenzisanayo, isixhobo esisodwa esidibanisa amazwi abasetyhini kunye namantombazana kunye namathuba angenasiphelo ohlalutyo lwedijithali.
pmn01a-subtext: Wamkelekile kwiDashbhodi ethi “Oko Kufunwa Lulutsha”! Esi sixhobo sokusebenzisana sinika ukubonakaliswa okubonakalayo kweempendulo kunye nokuqonda esikuhlanganisayo kubantu abatsha abaneminyaka eyi-10-24 emhlabeni jikelele. Ingundoqo yeli nyathelo ngumbuzo ovulekileyo: "Ukuphucula impilo-ntle yam, ndifuna ...". Abantu abatsha abavela kwihlabathi liphela bebephendula oku, besinika iimbono ezizodwa ngeemfuno zabo, amathemba, kunye nolangazelelo lwabo. Jonga idatha, fumana amabali ngasemva kwamanani, kwaye uhlanganyele nathi ekwandiseni amazwi abantu abancinci be-1.8 yezigidigidi kwihlabathi liphela. Ukufunda ngakumbi ngeli phulo, ndwendwela http://www.1point8.org.
midwife-subtext: Sabuza abazalisikazi ehlabathini lonke lo mbuzo: “Yintoni oyifunayo kakhulu kwindima yakho njengombelekisi?”
giz-subtext: Sabuza 10603 abafazi baseMexico lo mbuzo, “¿Qué es lo que más deseas o necesitas para encontrar empleo o un mejor empleo? Nceda, comparte sólo la petición más importante para ti.“, (Yintoni eyona nto uyifunayo okanye oyidingayo ukuze ufumane umsebenzi okanye umsebenzi ongcono? Nceda wabelane ngesicelo kuphela esibaluleke kakhulu kuwe.)
healthwellbeing-title: Yintoni abafazi abafuna ngayo impilo kunye nempilo
healthwellbeing-subtext: Sibuze abasetyhini kwihlabathi liphela, ukuba bafuna ntoni ukuphucula impilo kunye nempilo yabo.
wwwpakistan-subtext: Sibuze abafazi abangama-245311 basePakistan, ukuba bafuna ntoni ukuphucula impilo yabo kunye nempilo yabo.
giz-q1: Yintoni eyona nto uyifunayo okanye oyidingayo ukuze ufumane umsebenzi okanye umsebenzi ongcono? Nceda wabelane ngesicelo kuphela esibaluleke kakhulu kuwe.
giz-q2: Kufuneka enze ntoni urhulumente ukuze akuncede ufumane umsebenzi oliphupha lakho? Nceda wabelane ngesicelo kuphela esibaluleke kakhulu kuwe.
healthwellbeing-q1: Ufuna ntoni ukuphucula impilo yakho kunye nokuba sempilweni?
